# Screenshot and demo asset naming conventions:
#
#   dashboard-overview.png    — Main dashboard (logged in)
#   agent-console-scribe.png  — Scribe agent running
#   agent-console-trace.png   — Trace agent running
#   job-detail-timeline.png   — Job detail with SSE timeline
#   onboarding-flow.png       — 3-step getting started
#   demo.gif                  — Short animated demo (~15s)
#
# Image specs:
#   - Format: PNG for screenshots, GIF for animations
#   - Max width: 1200px (GitHub renders well at this size)
#   - File size: < 500KB per image, < 5MB for GIF
